# Cursor Rules

Always read PROJECT_CONTEXT.md before planning changes.

Before editing:
- inspect existing files
- explain the plan shortly
- change only necessary files

Coding:
- never rewrite whole files unless explicitly asked
- preserve existing functionality
- keep components small
- avoid duplicated logic
- avoid unnecessary dependencies
- use TypeScript types
- handle loading and error states

UI:
- mobile-first
- clean SaaS interface
- no visual clutter
- consistent spacing
- do not add random animations

Security:
- never expose API keys
- never commit .env values
- use environment variables